uistics_(journal)" title="Linguistics (journal)">Linguistics (journal)</a>.</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable" about="#mwt2" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"redirect","href":"./Template:Redirect"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"Linguist"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAw">"Linguist" redirects here. For other uses, see <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Linguist_(disambiguation)" title="Linguist (disambiguation)">Linguist (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<p id="mwBA"><span typeof="mw:Nowiki mw:Transclusion" about="#mwt3" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Use British English Oxford spelling","href":"./Template:Use_British_English_Oxford_spelling"},"params":{"date":{"wt":"August 2016"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBQ"></span><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:Use_British_English_Oxford_spelling_from_August_2016" about="#mwt3" id="mwBg"/></p>
